f(u)=\frac{1}{1-u}\Rightarrow f'(x)=\dfrac{(-1)(-1)}{(1-u)^2}=\dfrac{1}{(1-u)^2}
f''(u)=\dfrac{1.(-2).(-1)}{(1-u)^3}=\dfrac{1.2}{(1-u)^3}
f'''(u)=\dfrac{1.2.(-3)(-1)}{(1-u)^4}=\dfrac{1.2.3}{(1-u)^4}
f^{(n)}(u)=\dfrac{n!}{(1-u)^{n+1}}
